annotationA: CG6950, isoform A; Pyridoxal phosphate binding; kynurenine-oxoglutarate transaminase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: biosynthetic process
annotationB: Catalyzes the hydroxylation of L-kynurenine (L-Kyn) to form 3-hydroxy-L-kynurenine (L-3OHKyn). Required for synthesis of quinolinic acid
